msgctxt "104"
msgid "It's the Tojo Terror, Kazuma Kiryu, over at Smile Burger grabbing a bite to eat. Some dweeb next to me seemed kinda pissed that I was talking on my phone."
msgstr "It's the Tojo Terror, Kazuma Kiryu, over at Smile Burger grabbing a bite to eat. Some dweeb next to me seemed kinda pissed that I was talking on my phone."

msgctxt "116"
msgid "So I hit him with a, \"What's it to you, bitch!?\" That shut him up real good."
msgstr "So I hit him with a, \"What's it to you, bitch!?\" That shut him up real good."

msgctxt "128"
msgid "Heh, that'll teach him to pick a fight with a legend. Anyways, signing off.\\r\n"\n"　　　　　　　　　　　-Kazuma Kiryu, Dragon of Dojima"
msgstr "Heh, that'll teach him to pick a fight with a legend. Anyways, signing off.\\r\n"\n"　　　　　　　　　　　-Kazuma Kiryu, Dragon of Dojima"

